:H2.Appendices
:pc.The appendix segment of a document occurs following
the :hp2.&gml.appendix:ehp2. tag.
:I2 refid='ttappen'.ttappen
The appendix segment is very similar to the body segment, except that
:hp2.&gml.h0:ehp2.
:I2 refid='tth0'.tth0
tags may not be specified.
The usual convention is to use :hp2.&gml.h1:ehp2.
:I2 refid='tth1'.tth1
tags to name
the appendices and to use higher-numbered heading tags for
the sections and subsections within an appendix.
